# CODEOWNERS - Automatic Code Review Assignment
# 
# This file defines who will be automatically requested for review when a PR is opened.
# Users listed here will be automatically assigned as reviewers.
#
# Syntax: <file-pattern> @github-username @github-team
# 
# For more information, see:
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
# Replace @RamNull with actual GitHub username(s) or team(s)
*       @RamNull

# Java source code
*.java  @RamNull

# Configuration files
*.yml   @RamNull
*.yaml  @RamNull
*.xml   @RamNull
*.properties @RamNull

# Documentation
*.md    @RamNull

# GitHub workflows and actions
/.github/ @RamNull
